257
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:12,765
(MEN SHOUTING)

258
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:27,486
Sarge, south section. Fence one is down.

259
00:21:27,560 --> 00:21:29,688
Use the flamethrower. Short bursts.

260
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:33,122
