264
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:19,083
Good morning, Dr Caldwell.
Good morning, Dr Selkirk.

265
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,605
Good morning, Melanie.

266
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:24,604
Did you think about that cat?
The cat in the box?

267
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:27,365
