301
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:52,327
(SCREAMS)

302
00:24:52,440 --> 00:24:53,930
No! Leave her alone.

303
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,240
(COUGHS)

304
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,765
(HELEN GROANING AND COUGHING)

305
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,241
