- (MELANIE STRUGGLING)

317
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:46,488
There's a cranial strap on the left.

318
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:49,609
I'm not gonna cut around a cranial strap.

319
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:50,761
Do I re-dose her?

